WEBVTT

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:33.216
and what happiness were they seeking.

00:03:33.240 --> 00:03:41.060
Love is also a horizon of sorts and, thank
God, our movies never let us forget that.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:43.490
These lovers are no
different from those

00:03:43.490 --> 00:03:48.606
who take their longing to temples,
churches and mosques.

00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:53.056
A shrine has many different
meanings for people.

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:56.816
Some people go to tie
a thread, to ask for a boon,

00:03:56.840 --> 00:04:05.110
ask for a job, help in exams, success
in love, and some people go there to relax.